window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As a prisoner in the arena, my greatest battle won't be for my life. It'll be for the heart of a woman.</p> <p>Once I scented the human, she was mine. Every part of me hungered for her.</p> <p>To touch. To taste. To take.</p> <p>But she belongs to my enemy.</p> <p>Claiming her will cost me. I may sacrifice everything.</p> <p>My revenge. My life. My very soul.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
